.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, metal, hip-hop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, basketball, badminton, baseball
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
4. the fan of funk is the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the fan of metal is between the fan of electronic and the fan of funk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | metal           | electronic | hip-hop  |
| Sport         | tennis | baseball | basketball   | badminton |

