.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, pop, blues, dubstep
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski, airplane, tram
1. the fan of pop is the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the fan of reggae is between the person driving the skateboard and the fan of blues##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | pop | reggae | blues      |
| Transport     | airplane | skateboard    | jet-ski  | tram |

