.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, tennis, skiing, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, boat, car
1. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person driving the boat##2
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | surfing | parkour | skiing     | tennis   |
| Transport   | boat   | taxi     | car | skateboard |

