.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, bartender, fisherman, scientist
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile, trike, helicopter
1. the fisherman is between the person driving the jet-ski and the chef##2
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the chef##1
3. the scientist is on the right of the chef##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the chef is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | bartender | fisherman | chef | scientist |
| Transport   | jet-ski         | helicopter       | snowmobile    | trike         |

