.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, papaya, cranberry, blueberry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, volleyball, parkour, soccer
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
3. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person eating papaya and the person who's sport is soccer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | blueberry   | cranberry      | papaya   | watermelon  |
| Sport   | soccer | volleyball | parkour | rowing |

