.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, raspberry, artichoke, carrot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, comedy, martial-arts
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person eating raspberry is between the person eating carrot and the person eating zucchini##2
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | zucchini     | raspberry | carrot   | artichoke        |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | comedy   | mystery | martial-arts |

