.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, baking, reading, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, reggae, ambient, hip-hop
1. the fan of ambient is the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of techno is the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the fan of reggae is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is board-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | baking | reading | board-games | chess |
| Music-Genre   | ambient          | reggae     | hip-hop  | techno     |

