.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, firefighter, doctor, dancer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, family, fantasy, romance
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the firefighter##1
2. the dancer is between the person watching romance movies and the pilot##2
3. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
4. the pilot is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | pilot | dancer | firefighter | doctor     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | fantasy    | romance   | family |

