.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, spanish, colombian, argentine
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, van, train
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the argentine is the person driving the van##1
3. the colombian is between the person driving the van and the spanish##2
4. the argentine is on the right of the colombian##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | italian | spanish | colombian | argentine |
| Transport     | helicopter     | roller   | train | van  |

