.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, brazilian, australian
4 different pets are kept: cat, rat, chinchilla, fish
1. the american is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
2. the australian is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the cat and the argentine##2
4. the owner of the fish is the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | australian | argentine | american | brazilian |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | fish  | rat | cat      |

