.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, thai, brazilian, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, soccer, snowboarding, climbing
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the russian is the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is between the indian and the brazilian##2
5. the brazilian is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | russian   | indian   | thai | brazilian |
| Sport         | tennis | soccer | climbing     | snowboarding    |

