.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, traveling, collecting, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: mouse, dog, rabbit, horse
1. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the owner of the mouse and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | collecting    | woodworking     | cooking | traveling |
| Pet     | dog | horse | rabbit       | mouse     |

 